    "markdown": "---\ntitle: Workflow\n---\n\n\n\n## Operational Product Development Timeline\n\nOver the course of the year, the survey team is developing a variety of different data products. Planning and preparation for surveys happens in the late winter and spring, surveys occur in the summer, data validation takes place over the course of the survey and after the survey, and data products are produced through fall and late winter.  \n\n\n::: {.cell tbl-cap='Operational product development timeline.'}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"tabwid\"><style>.cl-0b895188{}.cl-0b732cdc{font-family:'Arial';font-size:11pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-decoration:none;color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.00);background-color:transparent;}.cl-0b732cf0{font-family:'Arial';font-size:11pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-decoration:none;color:rgba(56, 42, 84, 1.00);background-color:transparent;}.cl-0b732cf1{font-family:'Arial';font-size:11pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-decoration:none;color:rgba(65, 64, 129, 1.00);background-color:transparent;}.cl-0b732cfa{font-family:'Arial';font-size:11pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-decoration:none;color:rgba(57, 93, 156, 1.00);background-color:transparent;}.cl-0b732d04{font-family:'Arial';font-size:11pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-decoration:none;color:rgba(53, 123, 162, 1.00);background-color:transparent;}.cl-0b732d05{font-family:'Arial';font-size:11pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-decoration:none;color:rgba(52, 151, 169, 1.00);background-color:transparent;}.cl-0b732d0e{font-family:'Arial';font-size:11pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-decoration:none;color:rgba(61, 180, 173, 1.00);background-color:transparent;}.cl-0b732d18{font-family:'Arial';font-size:11pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-decoration:none;color:rgba(96, 206, 172, 1.00);background-color:transparent;}.cl-0b7baec0{margin:0;text-align:left;border-bottom: 0 solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 1